                        <interp inst="t18380226-name-870" type="given" value="SARAH"></interp>SARAH HAYWARD</persName>
                  </hi>. I received a bill from Mr. Northfield, in July, 1836—I paid the lad—this is the bill—I gave him the money for it—it is 4<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.—the boy put his name on it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
