                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable N</hi> 82.) I took the prisoner from in<lb></lb>formation—I told him that I took him for robbing his master of 8<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. odd—he said it was 2<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 5<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I never received the money for the bill, and never put the name on the bill, as I cannot write—my master knows I cannot.</p>
